      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 2 — Core Entities  (nouns → classes)\nData:      Card · Account · Denomination(enum)\nServices:  BankingService (fake backend) · AtmInventory (cash)\nContext:   ATM  (the coordinator)\nBehavior:  ATMState  → Idle · CardInserted · PinEntered   (STATE PATTERN)\n\nNote: Card is JUST an id — no pin, no balance (those live on the bank side).",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 2 — Core Entities  (nouns → classes)\nData:      Card · Account · Denomination(enum)\nServices:  BankingService (fake backend) · AtmInventory (cash)\nContext:   ATM  (the coordinator)\nBehavior:  ATMState  → Idle · CardInserted · PinEntered   (STATE PATTERN)\n\nNote: Card is JUST an id — no pin, no balance (those live on the bank side).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

