      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PASS 1 — First-go Attributes & Functions  (rough — expect mistakes!)\nCard { number, holder, pin? balance? }        <- pin/balance MISPLACED\nAccount { accNo, balance, withdraw() }\nAtmInventory { map<denom,count>, insertNotes(), withdrawNotes(d,c) }\nAtmState { insertCard(), enterPin(), withdraw() ... }   <- no params? no context?\n\nWHAT'S STILL MISSING (you won't see it yet):\n  · how does a state reach inventory / bank / change state?\n  · where does 'pinAttempts' live?   · who computes the note breakdown?\n  · withdraw order (debit vs dispense)?",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PASS 1 — First-go Attributes & Functions  (rough — expect mistakes!)\nCard { number, holder, pin? balance? }        <- pin/balance MISPLACED\nAccount { accNo, balance, withdraw() }\nAtmInventory { map<denom,count>, insertNotes(), withdrawNotes(d,c) }\nAtmState { insertCard(), enterPin(), withdraw() ... }   <- no params? no context?\n\nWHAT'S STILL MISSING (you won't see it yet):\n  · how does a state reach inventory / bank / change state?\n  · where does 'pinAttempts' live?   · who computes the note breakdown?\n  · withdraw order (debit vs dispense)?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

