    {
      "id": "text-5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220,
      "y": 1625,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 330,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1013,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 13,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PASS 3 — Code  (the last 20% of correctness)\nATM = pure coordinator: every op is a 1-line delegate to currentState.\nStates decide their OWN transition: atm.setState(new PinEnteredState(atm)).\nContext clears its own data: atm.resetCard() / resetSession().\n\nWITHDRAW — guarded ordering (the classic trap):\n  1) canDispense(amount)   <- read-only check FIRST, bail if false\n  2) bankingService.withdraw(card, amount)   <- debit (may throw)\n  3) inventory.dispenseNotes(amount)          <- hand out cash\n  RULE: do reversible checks BEFORE the irreversible mutation.\nInventory = two-phase greedy: computePlan() (no mutate) -> commit on success.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PASS 3 — Code  (the last 20% of correctness)\nATM = pure coordinator: every op is a 1-line delegate to currentState.\nStates decide their OWN transition: atm.setState(new PinEnteredState(atm)).\nContext clears its own data: atm.resetCard() / resetSession().\n\nWITHDRAW — guarded ordering (the classic trap):\n  1) canDispense(amount)   <- read-only check FIRST, bail if false\n  2) bankingService.withdraw(card, amount)   <- debit (may throw)\n  3) inventory.dispenseNotes(amount)          <- hand out cash\n  RULE: do reversible checks BEFORE the irreversible mutation.\nInventory = two-phase greedy: computePlan() (no mutate) -> commit on success.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

